# Terraform
**/.terraform/          # downloaded provider plugins (large, regenerated by init)
*.tfstate               # local state — we use GCS remote backend instead
*.tfstate.backup
*.tfplan                # binary plan files — not human-readable, regenerated by CI
# NOTE: .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT ignored — commit it so
# everyone gets the same provider version (like package-lock.json)
